article.story: MONROE, La. -- — Kyle Hayman scored 27 points to lead Stephen F. Austin to a 68-60 victory over UL Monroe on Friday night. Hayman shot 10 of 19 from the field, including 5 for 9 from 3-point range, and went 2 for 5 from the line for the Lumberjacks (5-3). Myles Jenkins shot 5 for 10 and scored 11. Jalen Bolden led the way for the Warhawks (3-6) with 15 points, four assists and two steals. Tyreese Watson scored 14 and Makai Willis had 13 points and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
